trans-unit.source: Provides an attached property store for <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 연결된 된 속성 저장소에 대 한 제공 <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: VisualBasic allows for an instance of <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings> to be attached to the top level activity in a workflow defined in a XAML file, thus defining the settings for all <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601> and <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601> expressions in that workflow.
trans-unit.target: VisualBasic의 인스턴스를 고려한 <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings>XAML 파일에 정의 된 모든에 대 한 설정을 정의 하는 워크플로의 최상위 작업에 첨부할 <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601>및 <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601>해당 워크플로의 표현식에에서.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicValue%601> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicReference%601> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings>

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref> instance attached to the specified object.
trans-unit.target: 검색 된 <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"> </xref> 인스턴스가 지정된 된 개체에 연결 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref> instance attached to the specified object.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"> </xref> 인스턴스가 지정된 된 개체에 연결 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Attaches a <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref> instance to the specified object.
trans-unit.target: 연결 된 <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"> </xref> 인스턴스 지정 된 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The object to which the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref> instance is attached.
Attaches a <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref> instance to an object for use by its implementation.
trans-unit.target: 연결 된 <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"> </xref> 인스턴스 구현에서 사용 하기 위해 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: SetSettingsForImplementation exists for the activity author who is creating a new activity in a class.
trans-unit.target: 클래스에서 새 활동을 만드는 활동 작성자에 대 한 SetSettingsForImplementation 존재 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Any <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings> required by the new activity’s implementation should be attached to the activity in the constructor using SetSettingsForImplementation.
trans-unit.target: 모든 <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings>새에 필요한 활동의 구현은 SetSettingsForImplementation를 사용 하 여 생성자에서 활동에 연결 되어야 합니다.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings>

trans-unit.source: The object to which the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref> instance is attached.
Returns a value that indicates whether the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref> instance associated with the specified object should be serialized.
trans-unit.target: 나타내는 값을 반환 여부는 <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"> </xref> 지정된 된 개체와 연결 된 인스턴스를 serialize 해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"></xref> instance should be serialized; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>경우는 <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Activities.VisualBasicSettings"> </xref> 고, 그렇지 않으면 serialize 된 인스턴스 해야 <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>합니다.
